      "content": "i get that, but i'm not really looking to go to the doctor just for a supplement. i've seen people in wellness forums say that doing \"loading doses\" like 50k is actually standard for people with severe deficiencies. if i only do it for like 2 or 3 weeks, wouldn't that be fine to just jumpstart my system? it seems like a lot of effort for something that's just a vitamin.",
